Class Record.DefaultImpls

  • com.udeyrishi.pipe.repository.Record.DefaultImpls
  • Enclosing interface:
    Record<T extends Identifiable>

    public static class Record.DefaultImpls

    Represents a unique item, and its metadata, as present in a interface Repository.

    Concrete interface Repository implementations will have their own interface Record implementations.

    See Also:
